data.description: Conveniently located near the 60 Freeway and the Montebello Town Center, which means easy access to transportation and shopping options. The unit has two bedrooms and two bathrooms, making it suitable for a small family or individuals needing a bit of extra space. Good size master bedroom, which can accommodate larger furniture and offers a comfortable living space. It also has an attached bathroom for added convenience. The spacious floor plan, along with vaulted ceilings in the living room and dining area, provides an open and airy feel to the unit. The presence of a peaceful balcony off the living room is a great feature, offering a spot for residents to enjoy their morning coffee and some fresh air. The unit includes a one-car covered parking garage with storage cupboards, which is a valuable addition for storage and protecting your vehicle. Additionally, there is an extra parking space available. The condominium complex offers a sparkling community pool, which can be a fantastic place for residents to relax and unwind. The community clubhouse is another amenity that adds value to the property, potentially providing space for gatherings and events.
